:: choices {"position":"200,325","size":"100,100"}
This training will consist of two levels, your first level will be practcing your human habits!

We have given you a few simple actvities to start your transformation. Make sure to choose the activites that a normal human would most likely do, then you'll gain some humanity points! Failing to choose the right activity however, will result in you losing some points, so be careful!

What will you do?
- [[Indulge in fast food->gain]]
- [[Lick your forehead->lose]]
- [[Listen to pop music->gain]]
- [[Eat a human being->lose]]
- [[Binge-watch movies->gain]]

<!--I didn't really know what to put for the options so they r kind of random haha-->


:: choices2 {"position":"225,625","size":"100,100"}
Congrats on making it to the next level of your training! 

This level will be slightly different from the previous one, you will need to partake in some more advanced activities in order to strengthen your //human// mind.

Choose the option that would be more useful for understanding humans!
- [[Learn human emotions->gain2]]
- [[Over-analyze random objects->lose2]]
- [[Study history and culture->gain2]]
- [[Form a new language->lose2]]
- [[Practice casual conversations->gain2]]


