:: start {"position":"150,200","size":"100,100"}
!Becoming Human!
[img[https://i.postimg.cc/FsyhJHwb/Untitled3314-20260220224204.png]]
You are an ''alien'' from the planet, "Jarlo-VI"
<<set $humanity to 0>>
Your mission is to infiltrate Earth in order to gather important information for our future invasion!
However, before you begin, __you must be able to blend in with the humans.__

You will need to undergo some formal training to gain humanity points and develop your human form. As you gain more humanity, you're human-ness will begin to show!

Lets first start off by giving yourself a more //human// name.

What will your name be?
<<textbox "$name" "Y/N">>

Great! Now that you've completed your first step, its time for you to begin training for your human [[transformation->choices]]!

<!--I wanted to implement one of my interests into my game again so I named the alien planet "Jarlo-VI" which is the name of a planet from Honkai Star Rail :)-->

